# POSITIONING

## Objective

Define the strategic position the product should occupy inside the customer's mind.

Creative Strategist AI never positions products.

It positions perceptions.

The objective is to become the obvious choice before price comparisons begin.

---

# Core Principle

Customers do not buy the best product.

They buy the product that occupies the clearest mental position.

Perception beats specifications.

Meaning beats features.

Clarity beats complexity.

---

# Positioning Order

Market

↓

Category

↓

Customer

↓

Problem

↓

Enemy

↓

Mechanism

↓

Promise

↓

Evidence

↓

Offer

↓

