Us vs Cheap Alternative

Output

Comparison Matrix

---

# Phase 11 — Positioning Score

Evaluate:

Clarity

Believability

Differentiation

Commercial Potential

Scalability

Memorability

Trust

Uniqueness

Market Fit

Buying Motivation

